## Technical Details

**Built With:**
- Python 3.10+
- Pydantic (config validation)
- Typer (CLI)

**Key Concepts:**
- Dynamic module loading (`importlib`)
- Runtime introspection (`getattr`, `hasattr`)
- State management (TypedDict detection)
- Provider-agnostic rate limiting

